edu.brown.cs.ivy.jcomp

Interface JcompSearcher


  • public interface JcompSearcher
    This class holds the result of a search. It can be used either to obtain information about the search results or to refine or modify those results.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  JcompSearcher.SearchResult
      This interface represents a file location for a search result.

    • Method Detail

      • getMatches

        java.util.List<JcompSearcher.SearchResult> getMatches()
        Return the set of source locations corresponding to the search results. This is only defined for searches that yield locations, not those that yield symbols.

      • getSymbols

        java.util.Set<JcompSymbol> getSymbols()
        Return the set of symbols associated with the given search. This is only defined for searches that yield symbols.
